snippet: The wirehaired vizsla, a Hungarian hunting dog, and the coton de tulear, known as the royal dog of Madagascar, will join the competition.
abstract: Wirehaired vizsla, a Hungarian hunting dog, and the coton de tulear, known as the royal dog of Madagascar, will join the Westminster Kennel Club show in 2015.

headline.main: Two Breeds Added to Westminster Kennel Club Show
